{"tid":1362652,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]香港最多呢類人！","createTime":"2019-07-25T02:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T02:38:37.000Z","uid":275307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ff732857a14ce6ce6cadf58159e8813cb667a1de","tid":1362652,"uid":275307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:38:37.000Z","msg":"今日去茶記食早餐<br />\n見到隔離枱班師奶拎住份方向報<br />\n都以為佢狗口長不岀象牙架喇<br />\n<br />\n點知佢講左句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「林鄭講一句撤回咪無事囉」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我就繼續聽下佢有咩偉論啦<br />\n結果佢之後就開始話<br />\n搞還搞 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>唔好殃及池魚</strong></span>就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲加多句 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>最多咪留係屋企唔岀街</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我發現香港最慘既係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲識分對錯</span></strong></span>既人 選擇作壁上觀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔識分對錯</span></strong></span>既人(藍絲/建制) 岀黎歪理滿天飛<br />\n<br />\n究竟點先可以令呢班 <span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲識分對錯</span></strong></span>既人行岀黎<br />\n唔好再事不關己咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢班人會係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>成個運動成敗既關鍵</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}